4481/// Emit function which wraps the outline parallel region
4482/// and controls the arguments which are passed to this function.
4483/// The wrapper ensures that the outlined function is called
4484/// with the correct arguments when data is shared.
4485llvm::Function *CGOpenMPRuntimeNVPTX::createParallelDataSharingWrapper(
4486 llvm::Function *OutlinedParallelFn, const OMPExecutableDirective &D) {
4487 ASTContext &Ctx = CGM.getContext();
4488 const auto &CS = *D.getCapturedStmt(OMPD_parallel);
4489
4490 // Create a function that takes as argument the source thread.
4491 FunctionArgList WrapperArgs;
4492 QualType Int16QTy =
4493 Ctx.getIntTypeForBitwidth(/*DestWidth=*/16, /*Signed=*/false);
4494 QualType Int32QTy =
4495 Ctx.getIntTypeForBitwidth(/*DestWidth=*/32, /*Signed=*/false);
4496 ImplicitParamDecl ParallelLevelArg(Ctx, /*DC=*/nullptr, D.getBeginLoc(),
4497 /*Id=*/nullptr, Int16QTy,
4498 ImplicitParamDecl::Other);
4499 ImplicitParamDecl WrapperArg(Ctx, /*DC=*/nullptr, D.getBeginLoc(),
4500 /*Id=*/nullptr, Int32QTy,
4501 ImplicitParamDecl::Other);
4502 WrapperArgs.emplace_back(&ParallelLevelArg);
4503 WrapperArgs.emplace_back(&WrapperArg);
4504
4505 const CGFunctionInfo &CGFI =
4506 CGM.getTypes().arrangeBuiltinFunctionDeclaration(Ctx.VoidTy, WrapperArgs);
4507
4508 auto *Fn = llvm::Function::Create(
4509 CGM.getTypes().GetFunctionType(CGFI), llvm::GlobalValue::InternalLinkage,
4510 Twine(OutlinedParallelFn->getName(), "_wrapper"), &CGM.getModule());
4511 CGM.SetInternalFunctionAttributes(GlobalDecl(), Fn, CGFI);
4512 Fn->setLinkage(llvm::GlobalValue::InternalLinkage);
4513 Fn->setDoesNotRecurse();
4514
4515 CodeGenFunction CGF(CGM, /*suppressNewContext=*/true);
4516 CGF.StartFunction(GlobalDecl(), Ctx.VoidTy, Fn, CGFI, WrapperArgs,
4517 D.getBeginLoc(), D.getBeginLoc());
4518
4519 const auto *RD = CS.getCapturedRecordDecl();
4520 auto CurField = RD->field_begin();
4521
4522 Address ZeroAddr = CGF.CreateMemTemp(
4523 CGF.getContext().getIntTypeForBitwidth(/*DestWidth=*/32, /*Signed=*/1),
4524 /*Name*/ ".zero.addr");
4525 CGF.InitTempAlloca(ZeroAddr, CGF.Builder.getInt32(/*C*/ 0));
4526 // Get the array of arguments.
4527 SmallVector<llvm::Value *, 8> Args;
4528
4529 Args.emplace_back(CGF.GetAddrOfLocalVar(&WrapperArg).getPointer());
4530 Args.emplace_back(ZeroAddr.getPointer());
4531
4532 CGBuilderTy &Bld = CGF.Builder;
4533 auto CI = CS.capture_begin();
4534
4535 // Use global memory for data sharing.
4536 // Handle passing of global args to workers.
4537 Address GlobalArgs =
4538 CGF.CreateDefaultAlignTempAlloca(CGF.VoidPtrPtrTy, "global_args");
4539 llvm::Value *GlobalArgsPtr = GlobalArgs.getPointer();
4540 llvm::Value *DataSharingArgs[] = {GlobalArgsPtr};
4541 CGF.EmitRuntimeCall(
4542 createNVPTXRuntimeFunction(OMPRTL_NVPTX__kmpc_get_shared_variables),
4543 DataSharingArgs);
4544
4545 // Retrieve the shared variables from the list of references returned
4546 // by the runtime. Pass the variables to the outlined function.
4547 Address SharedArgListAddress = Address::invalid();
4548 if (CS.capture_size() > 0 ||
4549 isOpenMPLoopBoundSharingDirective(D.getDirectiveKind())) {
4550 SharedArgListAddress = CGF.EmitLoadOfPointer(
4551 GlobalArgs, CGF.getContext()
4552 .getPointerType(CGF.getContext().getPointerType(
4553 CGF.getContext().VoidPtrTy))
4554 .castAs<PointerType>());
4555 }
4556 unsigned Idx = 0;
4557 if (isOpenMPLoopBoundSharingDirective(D.getDirectiveKind())) {
4558 Address Src = Bld.CreateConstInBoundsGEP(SharedArgListAddress, Idx);
4559 Address TypedAddress = Bld.CreatePointerBitCastOrAddrSpaceCast(
4560 Src, CGF.SizeTy->getPointerTo());
4561 llvm::Value *LB = CGF.EmitLoadOfScalar(
4562 TypedAddress,
4563 /*Volatile=*/false,
4564 CGF.getContext().getPointerType(CGF.getContext().getSizeType()),
4565 cast<OMPLoopDirective>(D).getLowerBoundVariable()->getExprLoc());
4566 Args.emplace_back(LB);
4567 ++Idx;
4568 Src = Bld.CreateConstInBoundsGEP(SharedArgListAddress, Idx);
4569 TypedAddress = Bld.CreatePointerBitCastOrAddrSpaceCast(
4570 Src, CGF.SizeTy->getPointerTo());
4571 llvm::Value *UB = CGF.EmitLoadOfScalar(
4572 TypedAddress,
4573 /*Volatile=*/false,
4574 CGF.getContext().getPointerType(CGF.getContext().getSizeType()),
4575 cast<OMPLoopDirective>(D).getUpperBoundVariable()->getExprLoc());
4576 Args.emplace_back(UB);
4577 ++Idx;
4578 }
4579 if (CS.capture_size() > 0) {
4580 ASTContext &CGFContext = CGF.getContext();
4581 for (unsigned I = 0, E = CS.capture_size(); I < E; ++I, ++CI, ++CurField) {
4582 QualType ElemTy = CurField->getType();
4583 Address Src = Bld.CreateConstInBoundsGEP(SharedArgListAddress, I + Idx);
4584 Address TypedAddress = Bld.CreatePointerBitCastOrAddrSpaceCast(
4585 Src, CGF.ConvertTypeForMem(CGFContext.getPointerType(ElemTy)));
4586 llvm::Value *Arg = CGF.EmitLoadOfScalar(TypedAddress,
4587 /*Volatile=*/false,
4588 CGFContext.getPointerType(ElemTy),
4589 CI->getLocation());
4590 if (CI->capturesVariableByCopy() &&
4591 !CI->getCapturedVar()->getType()->isAnyPointerType()) {
4592 Arg = castValueToType(CGF, Arg, ElemTy, CGFContext.getUIntPtrType(),
4593 CI->getLocation());
4594 }
4595 Args.emplace_back(Arg);
4596 }
4597 }
4598
4599 emitOutlinedFunctionCall(CGF, D.getBeginLoc(), OutlinedParallelFn, Args);
4600 CGF.FinishFunction();
4601 return Fn;
4602}
4603
4604void CGOpenMPRuntimeNVPTX::emitFunctionProlog(CodeGenFunction &CGF,
4605 const Decl *D) {
4606 if (getDataSharingMode(CGM) != CGOpenMPRuntimeNVPTX::Generic)
4607 return;
4608
4609 assert(D && "Expected function or captured|block decl.");
4610 assert(FunctionGlobalizedDecls.count(CGF.CurFn) == 0 &&
4611 "Function is registered already.");
4612 assert((!TeamAndReductions.first || TeamAndReductions.first == D) &&
4613 "Team is set but not processed.");
4614 const Stmt *Body = nullptr;
4615 bool NeedToDelayGlobalization = false;
4616 if (const auto *FD = dyn_cast<FunctionDecl>(D)) {
4617 Body = FD->getBody();
4618 } else if (const auto *BD = dyn_cast<BlockDecl>(D)) {
4619 Body = BD->getBody();
4620 } else if (const auto *CD = dyn_cast<CapturedDecl>(D)) {
4621 Body = CD->getBody();
4622 NeedToDelayGlobalization = CGF.CapturedStmtInfo->getKind() == CR_OpenMP;
4623 if (NeedToDelayGlobalization &&
4624 getExecutionMode() == CGOpenMPRuntimeNVPTX::EM_SPMD)
4625 return;
4626 }
4627 if (!Body)
4628 return;
4629 CheckVarsEscapingDeclContext VarChecker(CGF, TeamAndReductions.second);
4630 VarChecker.Visit(Body);
4631 const RecordDecl *GlobalizedVarsRecord =
4632 VarChecker.getGlobalizedRecord(IsInTTDRegion);
4633 TeamAndReductions.first = nullptr;
4634 TeamAndReductions.second.clear();
4635 ArrayRef<const ValueDecl *> EscapedVariableLengthDecls =
4636 VarChecker.getEscapedVariableLengthDecls();
4637 if (!GlobalizedVarsRecord && EscapedVariableLengthDecls.empty())
4638 return;
4639 auto I = FunctionGlobalizedDecls.try_emplace(CGF.CurFn).first;
4640 I->getSecond().MappedParams =
4641 llvm::make_unique<CodeGenFunction::OMPMapVars>();
4642 I->getSecond().GlobalRecord = GlobalizedVarsRecord;
4643 I->getSecond().EscapedParameters.insert(
4644 VarChecker.getEscapedParameters().begin(),
4645 VarChecker.getEscapedParameters().end());
4646 I->getSecond().EscapedVariableLengthDecls.append(
4647 EscapedVariableLengthDecls.begin(), EscapedVariableLengthDecls.end());
4648 DeclToAddrMapTy &Data = I->getSecond().LocalVarData;
4649 for (const ValueDecl *VD : VarChecker.getEscapedDecls()) {
4650 assert(VD->isCanonicalDecl() && "Expected canonical declaration");
4651 const FieldDecl *FD = VarChecker.getFieldForGlobalizedVar(VD);
4652 Data.insert(std::make_pair(VD, MappedVarData(FD, IsInTTDRegion)));
4653 }
4654 if (!IsInTTDRegion && !NeedToDelayGlobalization && !IsInParallelRegion) {
4655 CheckVarsEscapingDeclContext VarChecker(CGF, llvm::None);
4656 VarChecker.Visit(Body);
4657 I->getSecond().SecondaryGlobalRecord =
4658 VarChecker.getGlobalizedRecord(/*IsInTTDRegion=*/true);
4659 I->getSecond().SecondaryLocalVarData.emplace();
4660 DeclToAddrMapTy &Data = I->getSecond().SecondaryLocalVarData.getValue();
4661 for (const ValueDecl *VD : VarChecker.getEscapedDecls()) {
4662 assert(VD->isCanonicalDecl() && "Expected canonical declaration");
4663 const FieldDecl *FD = VarChecker.getFieldForGlobalizedVar(VD);
4664 Data.insert(
4665 std::make_pair(VD, MappedVarData(FD, /*IsInTTDRegion=*/true)));
4666 }
4667 }
4668 if (!NeedToDelayGlobalization) {
4669 emitGenericVarsProlog(CGF, D->getBeginLoc(), /*WithSPMDCheck=*/true);
4670 struct GlobalizationScope final : EHScopeStack::Cleanup {
4671 GlobalizationScope() = default;
4672
4673 void Emit(CodeGenFunction &CGF, Flags flags) override {
4674 static_cast<CGOpenMPRuntimeNVPTX &>(CGF.CGM.getOpenMPRuntime())
4675 .emitGenericVarsEpilog(CGF, /*WithSPMDCheck=*/true);
4676 }
4677 };
4678 CGF.EHStack.pushCleanup<GlobalizationScope>(NormalAndEHCleanup);
4679 }
4680}
4681
4682Address CGOpenMPRuntimeNVPTX::getAddressOfLocalVariable(CodeGenFunction &CGF,
4683 const VarDecl *VD) {
4684 if (VD && VD->hasAttr<OMPAllocateDeclAttr>()) {
4685 const auto *A = VD->getAttr<OMPAllocateDeclAttr>();
4686 switch (A->getAllocatorType()) {
4687 // Use the default allocator here as by default local vars are
4688 // threadlocal.
4689 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPDefaultMemAlloc:
4690 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPThreadMemAlloc:
4691 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPHighBWMemAlloc:
4692 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPLowLatMemAlloc:
4693 // Follow the user decision - use default allocation.
4694 return Address::invalid();
4695 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPUserDefinedMemAlloc:
4696 // TODO: implement aupport for user-defined allocators.
4697 return Address::invalid();
4698 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPConstMemAlloc: {
4699 llvm::Type *VarTy = CGF.ConvertTypeForMem(VD->getType());
4700 auto *GV = new llvm::GlobalVariable(
4701 CGM.getModule(), VarTy, /*isConstant=*/false,
4702 llvm::GlobalValue::InternalLinkage,
4703 llvm::Constant::getNullValue(VarTy), VD->getName(),
4704 /*InsertBefore=*/nullptr, llvm::GlobalValue::NotThreadLocal,
4705 CGM.getContext().getTargetAddressSpace(LangAS::cuda_constant));
4706 CharUnits Align = CGM.getContext().getDeclAlign(VD);
4707 GV->setAlignment(Align.getQuantity());
4708 return Address(GV, Align);
4709 }
4710 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPPTeamMemAlloc: {
4711 llvm::Type *VarTy = CGF.ConvertTypeForMem(VD->getType());
4712 auto *GV = new llvm::GlobalVariable(
4713 CGM.getModule(), VarTy, /*isConstant=*/false,
4714 llvm::GlobalValue::InternalLinkage,
4715 llvm::Constant::getNullValue(VarTy), VD->getName(),
4716 /*InsertBefore=*/nullptr, llvm::GlobalValue::NotThreadLocal,
4717 CGM.getContext().getTargetAddressSpace(LangAS::cuda_shared));
4718 CharUnits Align = CGM.getContext().getDeclAlign(VD);
4719 GV->setAlignment(Align.getQuantity());
4720 return Address(GV, Align);
4721 }
4722 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPLargeCapMemAlloc:
4723 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPCGroupMemAlloc: {
4724 llvm::Type *VarTy = CGF.ConvertTypeForMem(VD->getType());
4725 auto *GV = new llvm::GlobalVariable(
4726 CGM.getModule(), VarTy, /*isConstant=*/false,
4727 llvm::GlobalValue::InternalLinkage,
4728 llvm::Constant::getNullValue(VarTy), VD->getName());
4729 CharUnits Align = CGM.getContext().getDeclAlign(VD);
4730 GV->setAlignment(Align.getQuantity());
4731 return Address(GV, Align);
4732 }
4733 }
4734 }
4735
4736 if (getDataSharingMode(CGM) != CGOpenMPRuntimeNVPTX::Generic)
4737 return Address::invalid();
4738
4739 VD = VD->getCanonicalDecl();
4740 auto I = FunctionGlobalizedDecls.find(CGF.CurFn);
4741 if (I == FunctionGlobalizedDecls.end())
4742 return Address::invalid();
4743 auto VDI = I->getSecond().LocalVarData.find(VD);
4744 if (VDI != I->getSecond().LocalVarData.end())
4745 return VDI->second.PrivateAddr;
4746 if (VD->hasAttrs()) {
4747 for (specific_attr_iterator<OMPReferencedVarAttr> IT(VD->attr_begin()),
4748 E(VD->attr_end());
4749 IT != E; ++IT) {
4750 auto VDI = I->getSecond().LocalVarData.find(
4751 cast<VarDecl>(cast<DeclRefExpr>(IT->getRef())->getDecl())
4752 ->getCanonicalDecl());
4753 if (VDI != I->getSecond().LocalVarData.end())
4754 return VDI->second.PrivateAddr;
4755 }
4756 }
4757
4758 return Address::invalid();
4759}

4761void CGOpenMPRuntimeNVPTX::functionFinished(CodeGenFunction &CGF) {
4762 FunctionGlobalizedDecls.erase(CGF.CurFn);
4763 CGOpenMPRuntime::functionFinished(CGF);
4764}

4767 CodeGenFunction &CGF, const OMPLoopDirective &S,
4768 OpenMPDistScheduleClauseKind &ScheduleKind,

4770 if (getExecutionMode() == CGOpenMPRuntimeNVPTX::EM_SPMD) {
4771 ScheduleKind = OMPC_DIST_SCHEDULE_static;
4772 Chunk = CGF.EmitScalarConversion(getNVPTXNumThreads(CGF),

4774 S.getIterationVariable()->getType(), S.getBeginLoc());
4775 return;
4776 }
4777 CGOpenMPRuntime::getDefaultDistScheduleAndChunk(
4778 CGF, S, ScheduleKind, Chunk);
4779}

4793void CGOpenMPRuntimeNVPTX::adjustTargetSpecificDataForLambdas(
4794 CodeGenFunction &CGF, const OMPExecutableDirective &D) const {
4795 assert(isOpenMPTargetExecutionDirective(D.getDirectiveKind()) &&
4796 " Expected target-based directive.");
4797 const CapturedStmt *CS = D.getCapturedStmt(OMPD_target);
4798 for (const CapturedStmt::Capture &C : CS->captures()) {
4799 // Capture variables captured by reference in lambdas for target-based
4800 // directives.
4801 if (!C.capturesVariable())
4802 continue;
4803 const VarDecl *VD = C.getCapturedVar();
4804 const auto *RD = VD->getType()
4805 .getCanonicalType()
4806 .getNonReferenceType()
4807 ->getAsCXXRecordDecl();
4808 if (!RD || !RD->isLambda())
4809 continue;
4810 Address VDAddr = CGF.GetAddrOfLocalVar(VD);
4811 LValue VDLVal;
4812 if (VD->getType().getCanonicalType()->isReferenceType())
4813 VDLVal = CGF.EmitLoadOfReferenceLValue(VDAddr, VD->getType());
4814 else
4815 VDLVal = CGF.MakeAddrLValue(
4816 VDAddr, VD->getType().getCanonicalType().getNonReferenceType());
4817 llvm::DenseMap<const VarDecl *, FieldDecl *> Captures;
4818 FieldDecl *ThisCapture = nullptr;
4819 RD->getCaptureFields(Captures, ThisCapture);
4820 if (ThisCapture && CGF.CapturedStmtInfo->isCXXThisExprCaptured()) {
4821 LValue ThisLVal =
4822 CGF.EmitLValueForFieldInitialization(VDLVal, ThisCapture);
4823 llvm::Value *CXXThis = CGF.LoadCXXThis();
4824 CGF.EmitStoreOfScalar(CXXThis, ThisLVal);
4825 }
4826 for (const LambdaCapture &LC : RD->captures()) {
4827 if (LC.getCaptureKind() != LCK_ByRef)
4828 continue;
4829 const VarDecl *VD = LC.getCapturedVar();
4830 if (!CS->capturesVariable(VD))
4831 continue;
4832 auto It = Captures.find(VD);
4833 assert(It != Captures.end() && "Found lambda capture without field.");
4834 LValue VarLVal = CGF.EmitLValueForFieldInitialization(VDLVal, It->second);
4835 Address VDAddr = CGF.GetAddrOfLocalVar(VD);
4836 if (VD->getType().getCanonicalType()->isReferenceType())
4837 VDAddr = CGF.EmitLoadOfReferenceLValue(VDAddr,
4838 VD->getType().getCanonicalType())
4839 .getAddress();
4840 CGF.EmitStoreOfScalar(VDAddr.getPointer(), VarLVal);
4841 }
4842 }
4843}

4845unsigned CGOpenMPRuntimeNVPTX::getDefaultFirstprivateAddressSpace() const {
4846 return CGM.getContext().getTargetAddressSpace(LangAS::cuda_constant);

4848
4849bool CGOpenMPRuntimeNVPTX::hasAllocateAttributeForGlobalVar(const VarDecl *VD,
4850 LangAS &AS) {
4851 if (!VD || !VD->hasAttr<OMPAllocateDeclAttr>())
4852 return false;
4853 const auto *A = VD->getAttr<OMPAllocateDeclAttr>();
4854 switch(A->getAllocatorType()) {
4855 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPDefaultMemAlloc:
4856 // Not supported, fallback to the default mem space.
4857 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPThreadMemAlloc:
4858 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPLargeCapMemAlloc:
4859 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPCGroupMemAlloc:
4860 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPHighBWMemAlloc:
4861 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPLowLatMemAlloc:
4862 AS = LangAS::Default;
4863 return true;
4864 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPConstMemAlloc:
4865 AS = LangAS::cuda_constant;
4866 return true;
4867 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPPTeamMemAlloc:
4868 AS = LangAS::cuda_shared;
4869 return true;
4870 case OMPAllocateDeclAttr::OMPUserDefinedMemAlloc:
4871 llvm_unreachable("Expected predefined allocator for the variables with the "
4872 "static storage.");
4873 }
4874 return false;
4875}

4877// Get current CudaArch and ignore any unknown values
4878static CudaArch getCudaArch(CodeGenModule &CGM) {
4879 if (!CGM.getTarget().hasFeature("ptx"))
4880 return CudaArch::UNKNOWN;
4881 llvm::StringMap<bool> Features;
4882 CGM.getTarget().initFeatureMap(Features, CGM.getDiags(),
4883 CGM.getTarget().getTargetOpts().CPU,
4884 CGM.getTarget().getTargetOpts().Features);
4885 for (const auto &Feature : Features) {
4886 if (Feature.getValue()) {
4887 CudaArch Arch = StringToCudaArch(Feature.getKey());
4888 if (Arch != CudaArch::UNKNOWN)
4889 return Arch;
4890 }
4891 }
4892 return CudaArch::UNKNOWN;
4893}

4895/// Check to see if target architecture supports unified addressing which is
4896/// a restriction for OpenMP requires clause "unified_shared_memory".
4897void CGOpenMPRuntimeNVPTX::checkArchForUnifiedAddressing(
4898 const OMPRequiresDecl *D) {
4899 for (const OMPClause *Clause : D->clauselists()) {
4900 if (Clause->getClauseKind() == OMPC_unified_shared_memory) {
4901 switch (getCudaArch(CGM)) {
4902 case CudaArch::SM_20:
4903 case CudaArch::SM_21:
4904 case CudaArch::SM_30:
4905 case CudaArch::SM_32:
4906 case CudaArch::SM_35:
4907 case CudaArch::SM_37:
4908 case CudaArch::SM_50:
4909 case CudaArch::SM_52:
4910 case CudaArch::SM_53:
4911 case CudaArch::SM_60:
4912 case CudaArch::SM_61:
4913 case CudaArch::SM_62:
4914 CGM.Error(Clause->getBeginLoc(),
4915 "Target architecture does not support unified addressing");
4916 return;
4917 case CudaArch::SM_70:
4918 case CudaArch::SM_72:
4919 case CudaArch::SM_75:
4920 case CudaArch::GFX600:
4921 case CudaArch::GFX601:
4922 case CudaArch::GFX700:
4923 case CudaArch::GFX701:
4924 case CudaArch::GFX702:
4925 case CudaArch::GFX703:
4926 case CudaArch::GFX704:
4927 case CudaArch::GFX801:
4928 case CudaArch::GFX802:
4929 case CudaArch::GFX803:
4930 case CudaArch::GFX810:
4931 case CudaArch::GFX900:
4932 case CudaArch::GFX902:
4933 case CudaArch::GFX904:
4934 case CudaArch::GFX906:
4935 case CudaArch::GFX909:
4936 case CudaArch::UNKNOWN:
4937 break;
4938 case CudaArch::LAST:
4939 llvm_unreachable("Unexpected Cuda arch.");
4940 }
4941 }
4942 }
4943 CGOpenMPRuntime::checkArchForUnifiedAddressing(D);
4944}

4946/// Get number of SMs and number of blocks per SM.
4947static std::pair<unsigned, unsigned> getSMsBlocksPerSM(CodeGenModule &CGM) {
4948 std::pair<unsigned, unsigned> Data;
4949 if (CGM.getLangOpts().OpenMPCUDANumSMs)
4950 Data.first = CGM.getLangOpts().OpenMPCUDANumSMs;
4951 if (CGM.getLangOpts().OpenMPCUDABlocksPerSM)
4952 Data.second = CGM.getLangOpts().OpenMPCUDABlocksPerSM;
4953 if (Data.first && Data.second)
4954 return Data;
4955 switch (getCudaArch(CGM)) {
4956 case CudaArch::SM_20:
4957 case CudaArch::SM_21:
4958 case CudaArch::SM_30:
4959 case CudaArch::SM_32:
4960 case CudaArch::SM_35:
4961 case CudaArch::SM_37:
4962 case CudaArch::SM_50:
4963 case CudaArch::SM_52:
4964 case CudaArch::SM_53:
4965 return {16, 16};
4966 case CudaArch::SM_60:
4967 case CudaArch::SM_61:
4968 case CudaArch::SM_62:
4969 return {56, 32};
4970 case CudaArch::SM_70:
4971 case CudaArch::SM_72:
4972 case CudaArch::SM_75:
4973 return {84, 32};
4974 case CudaArch::GFX600:
4975 case CudaArch::GFX601:
4976 case CudaArch::GFX700:
4977 case CudaArch::GFX701:
4978 case CudaArch::GFX702:
4979 case CudaArch::GFX703:
4980 case CudaArch::GFX704:
4981 case CudaArch::GFX801:
4982 case CudaArch::GFX802:
4983 case CudaArch::GFX803:
4984 case CudaArch::GFX810:
4985 case CudaArch::GFX900:
4986 case CudaArch::GFX902:
4987 case CudaArch::GFX904:
4988 case CudaArch::GFX906:
4989 case CudaArch::GFX909:
4990 case CudaArch::UNKNOWN:
4991 break;
4992 case CudaArch::LAST:
4993 llvm_unreachable("Unexpected Cuda arch.");
4994 }
4995 llvm_unreachable("Unexpected NVPTX target without ptx feature.");
4996}
4997
4998void CGOpenMPRuntimeNVPTX::clear() {
4999 if (!GlobalizedRecords.empty()) {
5000 ASTContext &C = CGM.getContext();
5001 llvm::SmallVector<const GlobalPtrSizeRecsTy *, 4> GlobalRecs;
5002 llvm::SmallVector<const GlobalPtrSizeRecsTy *, 4> SharedRecs;
5003 RecordDecl *StaticRD = C.buildImplicitRecord(
5004 "_openmp_static_memory_type_$_", RecordDecl::TagKind::TTK_Union);
5005 StaticRD->startDefinition();
5006 RecordDecl *SharedStaticRD = C.buildImplicitRecord(
5007 "_shared_openmp_static_memory_type_$_", RecordDecl::TagKind::TTK_Union);
5008 SharedStaticRD->startDefinition();
5009 for (const GlobalPtrSizeRecsTy &Records : GlobalizedRecords) {
5010 if (Records.Records.empty())
5011 continue;
5012 unsigned Size = 0;
5013 unsigned RecAlignment = 0;
5014 for (const RecordDecl *RD : Records.Records) {
5015 QualType RDTy = C.getRecordType(RD);
5016 unsigned Alignment = C.getTypeAlignInChars(RDTy).getQuantity();
5017 RecAlignment = std::max(RecAlignment, Alignment);
5018 unsigned RecSize = C.getTypeSizeInChars(RDTy).getQuantity();
5019 Size =
5020 llvm::alignTo(llvm::alignTo(Size, Alignment) + RecSize, Alignment);
5021 }
5022 Size = llvm::alignTo(Size, RecAlignment);
5023 llvm::APInt ArySize(/*numBits=*/64, Size);
5024 QualType SubTy = C.getConstantArrayType(
5025 C.CharTy, ArySize, ArrayType::Normal, /*IndexTypeQuals=*/0);
5026 const bool UseSharedMemory = Size <= SharedMemorySize;
5027 auto *Field =
5028 FieldDecl::Create(C, UseSharedMemory ? SharedStaticRD : StaticRD,
5029 SourceLocation(), SourceLocation(), nullptr, SubTy,
5030 C.getTrivialTypeSourceInfo(SubTy, SourceLocation()),
5031 /*BW=*/nullptr, /*Mutable=*/false,
5032 /*InitStyle=*/ICIS_NoInit);
5033 Field->setAccess(AS_public);
5034 if (UseSharedMemory) {
5035 SharedStaticRD->addDecl(Field);
5036 SharedRecs.push_back(&Records);
5037 } else {
5038 StaticRD->addDecl(Field);
5039 GlobalRecs.push_back(&Records);
5040 }
5041 Records.RecSize->setInitializer(llvm::ConstantInt::get(CGM.SizeTy, Size));
5042 Records.UseSharedMemory->setInitializer(
5043 llvm::ConstantInt::get(CGM.Int16Ty, UseSharedMemory ? 1 : 0));
5044 }
5045 // Allocate SharedMemorySize buffer for the shared memory.
5046 // FIXME: nvlink does not handle weak linkage correctly (object with the
5047 // different size are reported as erroneous).
5048 // Restore this code as sson as nvlink is fixed.
5049 if (!SharedStaticRD->field_empty()) {
5050 llvm::APInt ArySize(/*numBits=*/64, SharedMemorySize);
5051 QualType SubTy = C.getConstantArrayType(
5052 C.CharTy, ArySize, ArrayType::Normal, /*IndexTypeQuals=*/0);
5053 auto *Field = FieldDecl::Create(
5054 C, SharedStaticRD, SourceLocation(), SourceLocation(), nullptr, SubTy,
5055 C.getTrivialTypeSourceInfo(SubTy, SourceLocation()),
5056 /*BW=*/nullptr, /*Mutable=*/false,
5057 /*InitStyle=*/ICIS_NoInit);
5058 Field->setAccess(AS_public);
5059 SharedStaticRD->addDecl(Field);
5060 }
5061 SharedStaticRD->completeDefinition();
5062 if (!SharedStaticRD->field_empty()) {
5063 QualType StaticTy = C.getRecordType(SharedStaticRD);
5064 llvm::Type *LLVMStaticTy = CGM.getTypes().ConvertTypeForMem(StaticTy);
5065 auto *GV = new llvm::GlobalVariable(
5066 CGM.getModule(), LLVMStaticTy,
5067 /*isConstant=*/false, llvm::GlobalValue::CommonLinkage,
5068 llvm::Constant::getNullValue(LLVMStaticTy),
5069 "_openmp_shared_static_glob_rd_$_", /*InsertBefore=*/nullptr,
5070 llvm::GlobalValue::NotThreadLocal,
5071 C.getTargetAddressSpace(LangAS::cuda_shared));
5072 auto *Replacement = llvm::ConstantExpr::getPointerBitCastOrAddrSpaceCast(
5073 GV, CGM.VoidPtrTy);
5074 for (const GlobalPtrSizeRecsTy *Rec : SharedRecs) {
5075 Rec->Buffer->replaceAllUsesWith(Replacement);
5076 Rec->Buffer->eraseFromParent();
5077 }
5078 }
5079 StaticRD->completeDefinition();
5080 if (!StaticRD->field_empty()) {
5081 QualType StaticTy = C.getRecordType(StaticRD);
5082 std::pair<unsigned, unsigned> SMsBlockPerSM = getSMsBlocksPerSM(CGM);
5083 llvm::APInt Size1(32, SMsBlockPerSM.second);
5084 QualType Arr1Ty =
5085 C.getConstantArrayType(StaticTy, Size1, ArrayType::Normal,
5086 /*IndexTypeQuals=*/0);
5087 llvm::APInt Size2(32, SMsBlockPerSM.first);
5088 QualType Arr2Ty = C.getConstantArrayType(Arr1Ty, Size2, ArrayType::Normal,
5089 /*IndexTypeQuals=*/0);
5090 llvm::Type *LLVMArr2Ty = CGM.getTypes().ConvertTypeForMem(Arr2Ty);
5091 // FIXME: nvlink does not handle weak linkage correctly (object with the
5092 // different size are reported as erroneous).
5093 // Restore CommonLinkage as soon as nvlink is fixed.
5094 auto *GV = new llvm::GlobalVariable(
5095 CGM.getModule(), LLVMArr2Ty,
5096 /*isConstant=*/false, llvm::GlobalValue::InternalLinkage,
5097 llvm::Constant::getNullValue(LLVMArr2Ty),
5098 "_openmp_static_glob_rd_$_");
5099 auto *Replacement = llvm::ConstantExpr::getPointerBitCastOrAddrSpaceCast(
5100 GV, CGM.VoidPtrTy);
5101 for (const GlobalPtrSizeRecsTy *Rec : GlobalRecs) {
5102 Rec->Buffer->replaceAllUsesWith(Replacement);
5103 Rec->Buffer->eraseFromParent();
5104 }
5105 }
5106 }
5107 if (!TeamsReductions.empty()) {
5108 ASTContext &C = CGM.getContext();
5109 RecordDecl *StaticRD = C.buildImplicitRecord(
5110 "_openmp_teams_reduction_type_$_", RecordDecl::TagKind::TTK_Union);
5111 StaticRD->startDefinition();
5112 for (const RecordDecl *TeamReductionRec : TeamsReductions) {
5113 QualType RecTy = C.getRecordType(TeamReductionRec);
5114 auto *Field = FieldDecl::Create(
5115 C, StaticRD, SourceLocation(), SourceLocation(), nullptr, RecTy,
5116 C.getTrivialTypeSourceInfo(RecTy, SourceLocation()),
5117 /*BW=*/nullptr, /*Mutable=*/false,
5118 /*InitStyle=*/ICIS_NoInit);
5119 Field->setAccess(AS_public);
5120 StaticRD->addDecl(Field);
5121 }
5122 StaticRD->completeDefinition();
5123 QualType StaticTy = C.getRecordType(StaticRD);
5124 llvm::Type *LLVMReductionsBufferTy =
5125 CGM.getTypes().ConvertTypeForMem(StaticTy);
5126 // FIXME: nvlink does not handle weak linkage correctly (object with the
5127 // different size are reported as erroneous).
5128 // Restore CommonLinkage as soon as nvlink is fixed.
5129 auto *GV = new llvm::GlobalVariable(
5130 CGM.getModule(), LLVMReductionsBufferTy,
5131 /*isConstant=*/false, llvm::GlobalValue::InternalLinkage,
5132 llvm::Constant::getNullValue(LLVMReductionsBufferTy),
5133 "_openmp_teams_reductions_buffer_$_");
5134 KernelTeamsReductionPtr->setInitializer(
5135 llvm::ConstantExpr::getPointerBitCastOrAddrSpaceCast(GV,
5136 CGM.VoidPtrTy));
5137 }
5138 CGOpenMPRuntime::clear();
5139}
